{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#7280: keep-alive 缓存了多个页面后，onMouted执行多次",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:25:20.146189+00:00",
  "text": "keep-alive 缓存了多个页面后，onMouted执行多次\n\n### Vue version\r\n\r\n3.2.45\r\n\r\n### Link to minimal reproduction\r\n\r\nhttps://codesandbox.io/s/musing-tristan-jjobbr?file=/src/views/components/Page2.vue\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n首次执行1次onMounted 打印,page1 但点击切换到page2, 再点击page1 会发现执行了多次onMounted\r\n\r\n### What is expected?\r\n\r\n希望只执行当前页面的onMounted,只打印一次\r\n\r\n### What is actually happening?\r\n\r\n执行多次onMouted\r\n\r\n### System Info\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### Any additional comments?\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/25605435/205841050-354c643a-77c9-4998-8cc9-9180204343f2.png)\r\n\r\n_No response_",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    "scope: keep-alive",
    "has workaround"
  ],
